verbose_text: Since the dual oxidases (DUOX) have specialized domains for the dismutation of O 2 -, and produce H 2 O 2 as substrate for peroxidation and other oxidation reactions, XREF_BIBR we also examined Duox1 and Duox2 mRNA expression as well as glutathione synthetase (Gss), p40, and p47 mRNA expression in DMSO treated groups.
